{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/8.png?t=1734773850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Reknum: Fantasy of Dreams</i> is a 2.5D adventure and exploration game that combines action and the magic of dreams. Join Cheri on her epic quest to uncover the secrets of a dream world filled with strange creatures, puzzles, and surreal landscapes. With hand-drawn frame-by-frame graphics and an instrumental soundtrack that captures the essence of a dream, every step of this journey is a work of art.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf19 <strong>2.5D Adventure:</strong> Explore a dreamlike world full of secrets in an action-packed 2.5D environment reminiscent of classic Metroidvania games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/1.png?t=1734773850\" />\ud83c\udf19 <strong>Hand-Drawn Art:</strong> Enjoy beautiful hand-drawn graphics frame by frame, giving the game a unique and charming style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/7.png?t=1734773850\" />\ud83c\udf19 <strong>Instrumental Soundtrack:</strong> Immerse yourself in an instrumental soundtrack that perfectly complements the magical and mysterious atmosphere of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/3.png?t=1734773850\" />\ud83c\udf19 <strong>Explore and Solve:</strong> Traverse fantastic landscapes, face mysterious creatures, and solve puzzles to uncover the secrets of the dream world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/6.png?t=1734773850\" />\ud83c\udf19 <strong>Challenging Gameplay:</strong> Gain new abilities and powers as you progress, facing enemies and obstacles that will test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/5.png?t=1734773850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an unforgettable adventure full of mystery, magic, and challenges. Are you ready to uncover the secrets of dreams and save the world trapped between them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734773850","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/page.bg.jpg?t=1734773850","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/00c34d29c05a803999af5f92a3a3a96dca19faa6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734773850","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/00c34d29c05a803999af5f92a3a3a96dca19faa6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734773850","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/8.png?t=1734773850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Reknum: Fantasy of Dreams</i> is a 2.5D adventure and exploration game that combines action and the magic of dreams. Join Cheri on her epic quest to uncover the secrets of a dream world filled with strange creatures, puzzles, and surreal landscapes. With hand-drawn frame-by-frame graph